Section 17.1: LilyPond

The LilyPond notation engraver can be used with LaTeX via the lilypond-book command. First lets create a LaTeX

document (with the ﬁle extension .lytex) to embed our music in:

\documentclass[letterpaper,12pt]{article}

\begin{document}

\begin{center}
    {\fontsize{24pt}{24pt}\textbf{Twa Corbies}}\\
